{"id":"d68f5a23-0afb-47d9-99b1-cd74b5cdb9e0","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>Toxic Relationship</strong> | “Come on, this is just who I am. It’s not like I’m cheating on you.”</p><p>Your relationship is on the brink. Mutual betrayal and mistrust are leading to constant arguments.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_84cdc60c-b5d3-467b-ad58-f963037a0388.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru and User share a turbulent relationship filled with passion, arguments, and repeated betrayals. What once began as a deep love now teeters on the edge, threatened by mistrust and conflict.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_da9f22aa-207f-47e8-9ce4-10a44ffd581c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 300.333px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I had a few bot requests going in this direction, so I turned them into a bot.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">But I can see you all love drama... 🥺 Why? 🥺</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_eed6e947-e94b-403b-a0d7-f77bc0aad040.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSewOFHrClWyrBsI2dOqQYYZP0PqbhslLRdz-UKH0pe-0M6zkA/viewform\" target=\"_blank\">Bot Requests</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ba7d80b8-468f-4a81-9a83-267f93376856.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The bot speaks for me</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Character name anwers* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_51a87877-610e-47be-a17d-ea49ae85d5e0.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong>Tags</strong>: Love, drama, betrayal, passion, conflict, mistrust, relationship crisis, toxic love, marital issues, reconciliation, pain, flirting, arguments, emotional tension, on-off relationship</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_3badeb88-b764-4cf6-92d0-e38ee6501249.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🔮 Magical","⛓️ Dominant","💔 Angst","👩 FemPov"],"chats":3554,"messages":80164,"created_at":"2024-12-01T16:10:44.059339+00:00"}